short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Mission Labs tab limiter - limits the maximum number of open tabs to 10.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Chrome extension designed for use with Active Directory Group Policy. 

Enforce a maximum limit of 10 tabs in Google Chrome Enterprise. 

Created by Mission Labs limited.
